cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.RO 

This paper deals with computer vision and reasoning, which suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories. The most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) since the paper focuses on visual reasoning tasks. The second most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) since the paper deals with equipping machines with high-level reasoning. The third most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) since the paper evaluates machine reasoning ability using modern computer vision. The fourth most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) since the paper involves language understanding in the context of visual reasoning. The fifth most likely sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics) since the paper deals with hierarchical representation, which is relevant to robotics.
